snippet.title: Java Subclass and Superclass Tutorial - Real College Example
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- In this video I explain subclasses and superclass in java. First we make a Shoe class, then create 2 subclasses, Running and Walking. Shoe is now the superclass of the 2 subclasses. 

I hope this helps you with your assignments related to the java subclass and superclass :) This is GREAT practice for these concepts ..

I hope you enjoyed java subclass and superclass tutorial! -
